{"tid":2516158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷終止就 7.21 襲擊向鄧炳強索償　法律代表周三開記者會交代原因","createTime":"2021-05-04T12:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T13:01:25.000Z","uid":21742,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6a180c2fd6544fee7e9b1846971411631e9586","tid":2516158,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/林卓廷終止就-7-21-襲擊向鄧炳強索償-法律代表周三開記者會交代原因/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E5%B0%B1-7-21-%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%90%91%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=cab31f8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E5%B0%B1-7-21-%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%90%91%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%2F&h=7c983518\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/林卓廷終止就-7-21-襲擊向鄧炳強索償-法律代表周三開記者會交代原因/</a><br />\n<br />\n因 47 人案正被還押的民主黨前立法會議員林卓廷，早前聯同元朗 7.21 襲擊傷者入稟控告警務處長鄧炳強，指警方無履行職責保護市民向警方索償，林卓廷決定終止民事索償。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷的法津代表何俊仁、黨友莊榮輝以及 7.21 傷者，明日會開記者會交代詳情和解釋理由；林卓廷方面指，林卓廷因民主派初選國安案被還押，之後透過代表諮詢法律意見和其餘 8 名原告人，最終決定終止民事索償案。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷本身是 7.21 襲擊傷者，他在去年 1 月開記者會，宣布聯同 8 名 7.21 襲擊傷者，入稟向鄧炳強民事索償。"},{"pid":"260376d3b18bd8e20a00eecc499bfe79f2cdc439","tid":2516158,"uid":289257,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"民主黨又投共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h